description: Number of series-parallel networks with n unlabeled edges, multiple edges not allowed.
comments: This is a series-parallel network: o-o; all other series-parallel networks are obtained by connecting two series-parallel networks in series or in parallel. See A000084 for examples.
references: J. W. Moon, Some enumerative results on series-parallel networks, Annals Discrete Math., 33 (1987), 199-226 (the sequence v_n).
links: Index entries for sequences mentioned in Moon (1987)
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Dec 20 2000
